tasabeh.NameE: Glory be to God and praise be to Him
Glory be to God and praise be to God
Glory be to God Almighty and praise be to Him

tasabeh.NameA: سُبْحَانَ اللَّهِ وَبِحَمْدِهِ ، سُبْحَانَ اللَّهِ الْعَظِيمِ
tasabeh.NameE: Glory be to God and praise be to Him, Glory be to God Almighty

tasabeh.NameA: لَا إلَه إلّا اللهُ وَحْدَهُ لَا شَرِيكَ لَهُ، لَهُ الْمُلْكُ وَلَهُ الْحَمْدُ وَهُوَ عَلَى كُلُّ شَيْءِ قَدِيرِ.
tasabeh.NameE: There is no god but God alone, with no partner. To Him belongs dominion and to Him is praise, and He is capable of all things.

tasabeh.NameA: لا حَوْلَ وَلا قُوَّةَ إِلا بِاللَّهِ
tasabeh.NameE: There is no power nor strength except in God
Praise be to God, Lord of the worlds

tasabeh.NameA: الْلَّهُم صَلِّ وَسَلِم وَبَارِك عَلَى سَيِّدِنَا مُحَمَّد
tasabeh.NameE: O God, may your blessings and peace be upon our master Muhammad

tasabeh.NameA: سُبْحَانَ الْلَّهِ، وَالْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ، وَلَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا الْلَّهُ، وَالْلَّهُ أَكْبَرُ
tasabeh.NameE: Glory be to God, praise be to God, there is no god but God, and God is great.
There is no god but Allah

tasabeh.NameA: سُبْحَانَ اللَّهِ ، وَالْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ ، وَلا إِلَهَ إِلا اللَّهُ ، وَاللَّهُ أَكْبَرُ ، اللَّهُمَّ اغْفِرْ لِي ، اللَّهُمَّ ارْحَمْنِي ، اللَّهُمَّ ارْزُقْنِي.
tasabeh.NameE: Glory be to God, praise be to God, there is no god but God, and God is great. O God, forgive me, O God, have mercy on me, O God, grant me.

tasabeh.NameA: اللَّهُ أَكْبَرُ كَبِيرًا ، وَالْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ كَثِيرًا ، وَسُبْحَانَ اللَّهِ بُكْرَةً وَأَصِيلاً.
tasabeh.NameE: God is most great, and praise be to God greatly, and glory be to God tomorrow and at evening.

tasabeh.NameA: اللَّهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلَى مُحَمَّدٍ وَعَلَى آلِ مُحَمَّدٍ كَمَا صَلَّيْتَ عَلَى إِبْرَاهِيمَ , وَعَلَى آلِ إِبْرَاهِيمَ إِنَّكَ حَمِيدٌ مَجِيدٌ , اللَّهُمَّ بَارِكْ عَلَى مُحَمَّدٍ وَعَلَى آلِ مُحَمَّدٍ كَمَا بَارَكْتَ عَلَى إِبْرَاهِيمَ وَعَلَى آلِ إِبْرَاهِيمَ إِنَّكَ حَمِيدٌ مَجِيدٌ.
tasabeh.NameE: O God, bless Muhammad and the family of Muhammad as You blessed Abraham and the family of Abraham. Indeed, You are Praiseworthy and Glorious. O God, bless Muhammad and the family of Muhammad in abundance. You have blessed Abraham and the family of Abraham. Indeed, You are Praiseworthy and Glorious.
